{"search_data": "Uttar PradeshUP Migrant Labourers Skill Mapping 1st List Ready \u2013 Yogi AdityanathUttar Pradesh migrant workers first list after skill mapping is ready, check name in UP Migrant Labourers Skill Mapping 1st List, Yogi govt. to setup migrants commission, internship and placement to workers in the state to provide job security, employment opportunities available in MSME sector, ODOP Scheme and other rozgar yojanaTable of Contents  UP Migrant Labourers Skill Mapping 1st ListWork on Basis of Skills to Migrants in Uttar PradeshYogi\u2019s Two Pronged Strategy for Migrant WorkersGovt. to Provide Internship, Employment in UPUP Migrant Labourers Skill Mapping 1st ListThe state govt. of Uttar Pradesh has started the process of formation of a new Labour (Sewayojan and Employment) Welfare Board. Till date, more than 24 lakh migrant labourers have returned to UP amid Coronavirus (COVID-19) lockdown. Each of the migrants has been mapped as per their skills in the prepared UP Migrant Workers Skill Mapping 1st List. This list contains the name and skill mapping of around 14.75 migrant workers and the process is still ongoing which is to be completed in the next 15 days.CM Yogi Adityanath has ordered officials to provide apprenticeship to migrant labourers as per their skills. Also during the internship, migrant workers would also be given stipend. The officials have also got directions on providing insurance facility to migrants. The state govt. believes that there are employment opportunities in MSME sector, One District One Product (ODOP) Scheme and Vishwakarma Shram Samman Yojana.The labourers returning from other states would also be given facility of rental housing at lower prices under Affordable Rental Housing Complex Scheme. It is important to note that the list after skill mapping of migrant workers has been kept and maintained by the state government and is not available for public view till today.\u0938\u094d\u0915\u093f\u0932 \u092e\u0948\u092a\u093f